sources.title: Warhead
sources.description: Aka: "Prisoner In The Middle" A weapons expert is reluctantly sent on a mission to a middle-east warzone to locate a lost nuclear warhead and dismantle it before it falls into the wrong hands. But before he can complete his work, he is taken prisoner and thrust into the conflict, and finds himself looking out for more than just the warhead. Starring: David Janssen Taken From IMDB *Uploaded By FreeBmovies* Please visit my Internet T.V Channel Classic Cinema Fact: This Is John O' Connor 's Only Directed Film
